sentences: Lai Meiyun (Chinese: 赖美云; born 7 July 1998), is a Chinese Singer signed under Qigu Culture.
Meiyun has studied in Shenzhen High School from 2013 to 2016.
In October 2014, Meiyun auditioned for a position in S.I.N. G and was accepted as a trainee after ranking in the top 10.

sentences: On August 10, 2015, Meiyun debuted as part of S.I.N. G with the single "青春的告白".

sentences: She then emerged 6th in the final rankings and debuted with members from other companies to form Rocket Girls 101 on June 23, 2018.

On January 12, 2019, with the Rocket Girl 101 held "2019 Rocket Girl 101 Flying Concert" in Shanghai; On July 12, released the first individual Single "It's Raining"("下雨了"), which is included in the Rocket Girl 101 newly released album "立风”.

On January 12, 2019, with the Rocket Girl 101 held "2019 Rocket Girl 101 Flying Concert" in Shanghai; On July 12, released the first individual Single "It's Raining"("下雨了"), which is included in the Rocket Girl 101 newly released album "立风”.
On June 23, 2020, Meiyun graduated from Rocket Girls 101.

On June 24, 2020, just after graduation from Rocket Girls 101, Meiyun's personal studio was founded and released her first Single as a solo artist, "Girls and Crown"("女孩与王冠“), Meiyun begins her solo career.
On December 13, Meiyun began a half-year professional training course on physique, vocal and dance with the group.

sentences: 2018-2020: Produce 101 and Rocket Girls 101

On January 12, 2019, with the Rocket Girl 101 held "2019 Rocket Girl 101 Flying Concert" in Shanghai; On July 12, released the first individual Single "It's Raining"("下雨了"), which is included in the Rocket Girl 101 newly released album "立风”.
On November 22, released her second Single "Not Tiny"("不渺小"), which is an award for her 2nd sales contribution to Rocket Girl 101's second album "立风”.
2020-Present: Solo Career =
On July 28, released her single"Wait"("等等") as the theme song of TV show Forget Me Not Café(忘不了餐厅) series 2.
On July 31, released "Every Time"("每一次") as the theme song of animated series "Fox Spirit Matchmaker"("狐妖小红娘·金晨曦篇").
On August 3, released "Wild Girl"("野生姑娘”) as the theme song of "Psychic Princess"("通灵妃“) series 2.
